<p><strong>Q: What is The Wolf of Stone about?</strong></p>
<p>A: Set in a medieval-inspired world, The Wolf of Stone follows the journey of Ferrous, a young man cursed to transform into a wolf. Forced to navigate a perilous world where he is both feared and reviled, Ferrous must confront his destiny and discover the true meaning of loyalty, sacrifice, and the human spirit.</p>
<p><strong>Q: How does the PDF format enhance the reading experience?</strong></p>
